{"tid":1622916,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶 + 新片] 辛灝年：我愛中国 你愛中共","createTime":"2019-10-04T17:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:42:25.000Z","uid":199048,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53259f66d68dcff31b28c5d7067059962cb74640","tid":1622916,"uid":199048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:38:02.000Z","msg":"2005年既野又係時候回下帶，百看不厭<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>辛灝年妙答挑釁提問 : 我愛中国 你愛中共（高清晰版）</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SSdJlJACKwc&amp;t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSSdJlJACKwc%26t&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjhT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=39a2df6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SSdJlJACKwc&amp;t</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另一條新片先係重點<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>辛灝年：和理的建立人民議會，勇武的保衛人民議會</ins></strong><br />\n臨時議會一直有人提出，但其實一直都唔係好有明確既方向，可以話係得個「講」字，但未必知點樣入手，佢提出咗呢場運動最終可能真係靠臨時議會。唯有臨時議會，由下而上，先可以同政府討價還價，先可以制衡政府，用人民一人一票選出黎既臨時議會，先可以順理成章否認現時立法會，甚至政府，直接實行雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n我paraphrase得可能有錯，詳情請大家去望望，厭長既話可以直接飛去<strong>[13:54]</strong>開始。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>辛灝年講堂：《感謝香港二》「時代革命」的主題和「議會革命」的方向</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kjPzht_pgCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkjPzht_pgCQ&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjhT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=2b7adf56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kjPzht_pgCQ</a><br />\n<br />\n另有仲有一同三，有興趣可以去睇埋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理的建立人民議會<br />\n勇武的保衛人民議會</span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">[size=6]<strong>五大要求，缺一不可</strong>[/size=5]</div>"},{"pid":"9b830f3c0ec9905975b1e3c52fdf0a136eeb667e","tid":1622916,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:38:44.000Z","msg":"聽日繼續快閃突擊<br />\n我地贏在人多機動性高<br />\n係屋企步行範圍內搞<br />\n唔好依賴任何交通工具<br />\n因為隨時可能封路封鐵<br />\n唔好等有狗<br />\n快閃突擊完就轉場<br />\n攰就返屋企食飯訓教回滿血再出過<br />\n政府會好快頂唔順<br />\n認同唔該用盡任何途徑spread開去<br />\n祝大家武運亨通<br />\n<br />\nBTW如果見人偷野就當係鬼獅鳥左佢"},{"pid":"5a3004802907134f4938c9f934d64103f3a264f8","tid":1622916,"uid":199048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大要求，缺一不可</div></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3b405c0246e241d932da4a7183b01e991ee2ff4d","tid":1622916,"uid":199048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:41:20.000Z","msg":"建立臨時政府前，先有臨時議會，<br />\n一人一票直接實行雙普選，才可服人。"},{"pid":"99968ceebf750a67d16d53652c207a5fcb68e1f6","tid":1622916,"uid":199048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:39:05.000Z","msg":"有啲長但睇咗去啦<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"ca272787cfa6cfb05ce008b5aaed860d4d5cecf6","tid":1622916,"uid":323855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"好大陣陰氣"},{"pid":"7d53f7f049e6202dc3cfc101119c0acfbf35b454","tid":1622916,"uid":199048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}